<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GuardianAgent - GitLab Integration Setup</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS v4 via CDN -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background-color: #EAEAEA;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#EAEAEA] text-slate-800 min-h-screen pb-12">

    <!-- Sticky Top Navigation -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#EAEAEA] border-b-2 border-[#4F6D7A] px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between pointer-events-auto" style="pointer-events: auto;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="p-2 bg-white border border-[#4F6D7A]">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#4F6D7A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-lg text-[#4F6D7A] tracking-tight">GuardianAgent</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] border border-[#4F6D7A] text-[#4F6D7A] px-1.5 py-0.5 ml-2 font-mono uppercase font-bold">v1.0.0</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Center links -->
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/dashboard' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                Review Dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="/setup/github" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/setup/github' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                GitHub Setup
            </a>
            <a href="/setup/gitlab" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/setup/gitlab' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                GitLab Setup
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="text-right hidden sm:block">
                <p class="text-[10px] text-[#4F6D7A]/60 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">User</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#4F6D7A]"><%= userEmail %></p>
            </div>
            <a href="/logout" class="py-2 px-3 border border-[#4F6D7A] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#4F6D7A] hover:bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 transition-colors" title="Logout">
                Logout
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div class="border-2 border-[#4F6D7A] bg-white p-8 mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4F6D7A] uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">GitLab CI Integration Setup Guide</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6 font-medium">Follow these steps to connect your GitLab projects to GuardianAgent.</p>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <!-- Section 1 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">1. Obtain Access Tokens</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700 font-medium">
                        <li>Go to your GitLab User Settings, select **Access Tokens** (or **Personal Access Tokens**), and generate a new token. Do not use restricted Deploy Tokens as they do not support API writing permissions.</li>
                        <li>Give the token a name and check the following scopes: **`api`**, **`read_repository`**, and **`write_repository`** to allow the orchestrator to read commits, apply patches, and post comments.</li>
                        <li>Copy the generated token immediately. It will not be shown again.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 2 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">2. Add CI/CD Variables to GitLab</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700 font-medium" start="4">
                        <li>In your GitLab project, go to Settings, then select CI/CD, and expand Variables.</li>
                        <li>Create a Variable named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">OPENROUTER_API_KEY</code>, paste your OpenRouter key, and configure: <strong class="text-[#4F6D7A]">Masked: Enabled</strong> and <strong class="text-[#DD6E42]">Protect variable: Disabled</strong> (so it runs on Merge Request branches).</li>
                        <li>Create a Variable named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">GITLAB_TOKEN</code>, paste your GitLab Access Token, and configure: <strong class="text-[#4F6D7A]">Masked: Enabled</strong> and <strong class="text-[#DD6E42]">Protect variable: Disabled</strong>.</li>
                        <li>Create a Variable named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">GUARDIAN_USER_ID</code>, paste your unique ID shown below, and configure: <strong class="text-[#4F6D7A]">Masked: Disabled</strong> (does not meet masking rules) and <strong class="text-[#DD6E42]">Protect variable: Disabled</strong>:</li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between border border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#C0D6DF]/10 p-3 font-mono text-xs">
                        <span>GUARDIAN_USER_ID: <strong class="text-[#DD6E42]"><%= guardianUserId %></strong></span>
                        <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('<%= guardianUserId %>'); alert('Copied User ID!');" 
                                class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#4F6D7A] text-white hover:bg-[#4F6D7A]/90 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer">
                            Copy
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 3 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">3. Create CI Configuration File</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700 font-medium" start="8">
                        <li>Open your project's <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">.gitlab-ci.yml</code> file in the root directory.</li>
                        <li>If the file does not exist, create a new one named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">.gitlab-ci.yml</code>.</li>
                        <li>Copy the job block snippet below and paste it into the file, then commit your changes.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="mt-4 relative border border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#FFFFFF]">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#C0D6DF]/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-[#4F6D7A]">
                            <span>.gitlab-ci.yml</span>
                            <button onclick="copySnippet()" 
                                    class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#DD6E42] hover:bg-[#DD6E42]/90 text-white text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer">
                                Copy Snippet
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <pre id="yamlSnippet" class="p-4 font-mono text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-slate-700 overflow-x-auto max-h-[350px]">stages:
  - test

security-scan:
  stage: test
  image: python:3.10-slim
  before_script:
    - pip install requests
  rules:
    - if: '$CI_PIPELINE_SOURCE == "merge_request_event"'
  script:
    - curl -sS https://raw.githubusercontent.com/soft-hive-group/guardianagent-autonomous-gitlab-security-orchestrator/main/guardian.py -o guardian.py
    - python guardian.py --project-id $CI_PROJECT_ID --mr-iid $CI_MERGE_REQUEST_IID --gitlab-url $CI_SERVER_URL
  variables:
    GUARDIAN_USER_ID: "<%= guardianUserId %>"</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        function copySnippet() {
            const code = document.getElementById('yamlSnippet').innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {
                alert('CI configuration job copied to clipboard!');
            }).catch(err => {
                console.error('Copy failed: ', err);
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
